  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Diet is known to play role in the complex etiology of UC.Patient with UC tend to adapt
      unguided dietary habits without the guidance of a dietician or physician (Dejong,M.J 2019).so
      identification of nutritional gaps is needed to facilitate the development of evidence-based
      dietary guideline and subsequently give correct dietary advice to UC patients(Haskkey,N et al
      2017).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
